reviews.customers_say: Customers find this sweater well-made, soft, and comfortable, with a nice pattern and true-to-size fit.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great, comfy, colorful sweater.
items.body: Lovely, colorful sweater that can be worn with a simple skirt. Length is as shown and I selected a small for my 5'2", 110 lb frame. Fits comfortably and similar to picture ad. Read more
items.author: Mikaela

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this sweater! Buy yours before they’re gone
items.body: I absolutely love this sweater! It's incredibly soft and stretchy, yet it returns to its original size perfectly. The stripes are attractive, and the color is fantastic. I've washed it 2 times; there was one instance when I dried it and thought it had shrunk, but it actually hadn’t. The second time I washed it, I laid it flat to dry because I didn't want to risk damaging it in the dryer, although I believe it would be fine. Honestly, it's so soft, looks amazing, and feels high-quality—all at a great price. I highly recommend you grab one before they sell out! Read more
items.author: Shelley M

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice everyday sweater
items.body: This sweater was better quality than what I expected. I went with a large because I wasn't sure how it would wash but I probably could have gone with a medium. (I usually wear a medium to a large - 5'4" #142). It was a little large but soft and comfortable. Fabric seems like it will be warm for winter - made of an acrylic blend. Good for everyday wear. I have washed it once, dried it flat and it looks pretty good. I would order another one in a different color. Read more
items.author: JLP

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable and stylish
items.body: Good fit, soft fabric, very comfortable. Washes really well. I don’t dry it, I prefer to hang it to dry. Fits perfectly. Does not fade. One of my favorites. Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great sweater
items.body: Very soft, great color (the dark green). And it fits well… I’m tall (5’11”) and the sleeves are long enough as is the body of the sweater. I highly recommend. Read more
items.author: Smithy

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love it but my last pic is to show how not to wear!
items.body: I’m a 47 year old mom. I weigh 128 lbs. i have large breast naturally and annoyingly. The feel of this top is very soft on. The inside is as soft as the out. I hate that about some tops that look soft and feel terrible on your skin. This one feels soft inside and looks soft outside. I bought the wine color for winter. It looks like a light red wine with a hint of raspberry for you winos. Not as dark as pic but very nice. It feels lightweight but still thick giving a good stretch without being at all see through. I saw many of the pics posted and I feel like maybe they aren’t wearing the sweater to benefit their figures. I find it looks better on me with the waist band down rather than tucked up. I like this sweater. I’m no model, I do have a bit of a mommy mid section but I am blessed with thinner legs. I wish my waist matched my legs but that’s just not the case. It’s all about how you wear it. I’m not paid to write this haha I just hate seeing pics of beautiful women wearing things maybe the not in a way to make them look their best. Sweater top is great and love the stretch so I can kind of pull the ribbed paternal part below my boobs to possibly make them look larger than my waist lol. Read more
items.author: Monishegone

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love the material & look.
items.body: Love the fit & feel. I ordered another in a different color. The material has a nice feel like cotton not flimsy as some others. It has a classy look for office or casual. Great value. Read more
items.author: Arlene

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great sweater!
items.body: Fantastic sweaters!!! So comfy! They don't lose shape, they are thick but not hot and heavy. Very flattering! Read more
items.author: Jennifer Roi

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: A White, A Navy Blue, A Army Green, A Black, A Light Blue, A Wine Red, A Purple, A Warm Apricot, Colorblock 276, A Green, A Light Brown, Colorblock 284, Orange, A Royal Blue. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
